Claude Code's Head of Product: &quot;The PM role is changing a lot. And it's changing really quickly.

The most important thing for building AI-native products is iterating quickly and finding a way to launch features every single week.

Putting less emphasis on making sure that you are aligning multi-quarter roadmaps with your partner teams, and more emphasis on, okay, how can we figure out the fastest way to get something out the door.&quot;

